description: Novelist Halle Butler understands our worst enemy is sometimes our own brain. Her dark, chaotic novel manages to be often hilarious yet relentlessly uncheerful.
title: Everything is the worst in this 'Banal Nightmare'

description: Ana is so excited that her abuela is coming to live with her — until it means saying goodbye to her babysitter. No More Señora Mimí is an ode to caregivers from Meg Medina and Brittany Cicchese.
title: Some babysitters are forever — just ask 'Señora Mimí'

description: Multiple people were shot on a highway north of London, Ky., on Saturday, the Laurel County Sheriff’s Office said, forcing the closure to a stretch of I-75.
title: Police search for person of interest after multiple people shot near Kentucky highway
